Sustainability and Innovation As a responsible custom home builder, Stone Creek Building strongly emphasizes sustainability and innovation. We incorporate eco-friendly materials and energy-efficient solutions into our designs. From energy-efficient HVAC systems to sustainable building materials, we ensure that your custom home is a testament to your style and a contribution to a greener future. In conclusion, Stone Creek Building is more than just a custom home builder; we are your partners in crafting the home of your dreams. With a legacy of excellence, a commitment to quality, and a dedication to sustainability, we invite you to embark on the journey of a lifetime with us. Contact us today to start turning your vision into the masterpiece that is your custom home in the heart of Portland, Oregon. She helped her station launch its award-winning investigative franchise, ‘Your Voice Your Station.’ Her series on Birmingham’s Bluestone Coke plant won an Alabama Broadcaster’s Association award, after she uncovered the plant was operating with air quality violations. Prior to that, Chloe spent four years in the Southern Tier of New York, where she was a Main Evening Anchor at the CBS affiliate in Binghamton. She created an award-winning series called ‘Contaminated,’ where she investigated health hazards in the community. Her reports on dirty water in Endicott, NY led officials to invest in infrastructure upgrades, improving water quality for residents. Chloe was born and raised on the Connecticut shoreline. She graduated from the University of Connecticut with degrees in Journalism and Communications. In her free time, Chloe is an avid tennis player. She enjoys hiking, playing with her dog Lulu, and traveling. Chloe is also a major foodie and is excited to explore Roanoke’s restaurant scene! The potential applications of quantum computing are vast and varied. For example, quantum computers could be used to optimize supply chains, develop new materials, and simulate complex biological systems. They could also be used to solve optimization problems that are difficult or impossible to solve with classical computers, such as the traveling salesman problem or the knapsack problem. Here! Dryer vent cleaning is an important task that every homeowner in Hawaii should take seriously. Neglecting this task can result in fire hazards, increased energy bills, and reduced dryer efficiency. With the warm climate of Hawaii, it’s essential to keep your dryer vent clean and functioning properly. In this article, we’ll be discussing the steps on how to dryer vent cleaning in Vancouver & Hawaii, so you can ensure that your dryer is running safely and efficiently. With the right tools and a little bit of know-how, you can easily clean your dryer vent yourself and save some money in the process. So, let’s dive in and learn how to clean your dryer vent in Hawaii and Vancouver. Disconnecting the Dryer: Before starting the cleaning process, it’s important to disconnect the dryer from its power source. This will prevent any accidental start-ups while cleaning. Wearing Protective Gear: To ensure your safety, it’s recommended to wear gloves and a dust mask while cleaning the dryer vent. This will protect your hands and lungs from dust and debris. Understanding the Dryer Vent System: It’s essential to understand the dryer vent system before cleaning it. This will help you to avoid damaging the system or causing harm to yourself. – Vacuum Cleaner: A vacuum cleaner with a long hose attachment is the first and most important tool you need to clean your dryer vent. It helps to remove lint, debris, and other blockages from the vent system.– Screwdriver: A screwdriver is needed to remove screws that hold the vent cover in place. A Phillips head screwdriver is typically required.– Duct Brush: A duct brush is a long, flexible brush that is used to clean the interior of the vent system. It helps to reach deep into the vent to remove blockages and debris.– Duct Cleaning Kit: A duct cleaning kit is a set of specialized tools that are designed for cleaning dryer vents. These kits typically include a duct brush and other cleaning tools that make the cleaning process easier and more effective. Having the right tools and supplies for cleaning your dryer vent will make the process faster, easier, and more effective. So, make sure you have everything you need before you start cleaning your dryer vent. ALSO READ: Volcanoes – Removing the Vent Cover: The first step in cleaning the dryer vent is to remove the vent cover. This is usually done by loosening the screws that hold the cover in place.– Cleaning the Vent Interior: Once the vent cover has been removed, it’s time to clean the interior of the vent. Use a vacuum cleaner and duct brush to remove any debris and lint from the vent.– Cleaning the Exterior Vent: Next, clean the exterior vent. This is usually done by using a vacuum cleaner to remove any debris and lint from the outside of the vent.– Reassembling the Vent Cover: After cleaning the vent, it’s time to reassemble the vent cover. Make sure to tighten the screws securely to prevent any future leaks. 1. Regular Cleaning Schedule: It’s important to clean your dryer vent regularly to ensure its efficiency and safety. A recommended schedule is to clean it at least once a year.2. Checking for Blockages: Regularly check the vent for any blockages or clogs. If you notice any, clean them immediately.3. Proper Loading of Dryer: Make sure to properly load the dryer to avoid any blockages. Overloading the dryer can cause clogs in the vent.4. Keeping the Area Around the Dryer Clear: Keep the area around the dryer clear of any flammable materials. This will prevent any potential fire hazards. Recap of the Cleaning Process: In this article, we’ve discussed the steps on how to clean your dryer vent yourself in Hawaii. The process includes disconnecting the dryer, wearing protective gear, using the right tools and supplies, cleaning the vent interior and exterior, reassembling the vent cover, and following maintenance tips to keep your dryer running safely and efficiently. Regular cleaning of the dryer vent can bring many benefits. It can prevent fire hazards, reduce energy bills, and improve the efficiency of the dryer. By cleaning the dryer vent regularly, you can ensure that your dryer is functioning properly and efficiently. Cleaning the dryer vent can be done easily and inexpensively by following the steps outlined in this article. By taking the time to clean your dryer vent, you can ensure its safety and efficiency, and avoid potential hazards and costly repairs. So, make sure to add dryer vent cleaning to your regular home maintenance schedule and enjoy the peace of mind that comes with a well-functioning dryer. Also known as Venus Pool, Maui’s Waioka Pond off the road to Hana is easy to miss unless you’re looking for it. From Monetary Systems to Resource-Based Economy One of the film s central themes is the call to shift from a monetary-driven society to a resource-based economy. Unlike the current model where money and market forces dictate resource distribution, a resource-based economy seeks to manage and allocate resources based on scientific assessment and technological advancements. The documentary explores how such a system could eliminate the barriers of scarcity, foster cooperation, and optimize resource usage for the benefit of all. Embracing the Global Paradigm Shift As Paradise or Oblivion delves into The Venus Project s vision, it underscores the urgency of embracing a paradigm shift on a global scale. Jacque Fresco s ideas advocate for transcending cultural, national, and ideological boundaries to address challenges collectively. The film compellingly argues that this collective effort is crucial to avoid a future marked by environmental devastation and societal collapse. Filling the Gap: The Call for Practicality While the documentary enthralls with its innovative proposals, some critics argue that it lacks a detailed roadmap for achieving The Venus Project s vision. Although the concepts are undeniably intriguing, skepticism arises regarding the practicality and feasibility of implementing such a radical societal shift. Paradise or Oblivion grapples with the challenge of addressing the existing barriers to change, including vested interests, resistance to transformation, and institutional inertia. The Realization of Possibilities In conclusion, Paradise or Oblivion is not just a documentary but a journey—an exploration of human potential and the search for a better future. It serves as a wake-up call for humanity to face its greatest dilemmas and collectively embrace change. Regardless of one s stance on The Venus Project s proposals, the film unquestionably sparks vital conversations about the direction of our civilization and the imperative to seek harmony with nature and technology. As the credits roll, the question remains: Can we unlock the potential to create a world where paradise triumphs over oblivion? This thought-provoking documentary encourages viewers to take part in shaping a shared vision for a future that embraces conscious change, compassion, and cooperation in preserving our planet and uplifting the human experience. www.thevenusproject.com More Higher Education » Tags: Higher Education Comparing Different Types of Custom Fixed Asset Labels Should You Consider a Hybrid? 'language': 'en', 'pageNumber': 0, 'neatVersion': '3.3b', 'inputText': 'In today’s competitive labor market, many industries are facing the challenge of labor shortages, making it difficult to find skilled workers to fill crucial roles. This shortage can have significant impacts on companies and contractors, delaying projects, increasing costs, and limiting growth opportunities. However, with the right strategies in place, it is possible to navigate labor shortages successfully and find skilled labor to meet your project needs. In this article, we will provide a roadmap on how companies and contractors can overcome labor shortages and attract skilled workers, even when the talent pool is not always full. To overcome labor shortages, it is crucial to have a robust recruitment strategy in place. Consider the following approaches to attract skilled workers: a. Expand Your Reach: Cast a wider net when seeking talent. Advertise job openings through various channels, such as online job boards, industry-specific forums, social media platforms, and professional networks. Reach out to local trade schools, vocational programs, and community organizations to connect with potential candidates. b. Offer Competitive Compensation: To attract skilled workers, ensure that your compensation packages are competitive. Research industry standards and adjust your offerings accordingly. In addition to salary, consider benefits, bonuses, flexible working arrangements, and opportunities for growth and advancement. c. Build a Strong Employer Brand: Cultivate a positive employer brand to attract skilled workers. Highlight your company’s culture, values, and opportunities for career development. Leverage social media platforms and online employer review websites to showcase positive employee experiences and testimonials. d. Develop Employee Referral Programs: Encourage your current employees to refer potential candidates. Offering referral bonuses or incentives can motivate your workforce to tap into their networks and recommend qualified individuals. When skilled labor is scarce, consider investing in training and development programs to bridge the skills gap. By developing the capabilities of your existing workforce, you can address immediate project needs and create a pipeline of skilled talent. Some strategies to consider include: a. Internal Training Programs: Develop internal training programs to upskill existing employees. Identify key areas of need and provide training opportunities to enhance their skill sets. Partner with industry experts, trade associations, or vocational schools to deliver specialized training programs. b. Apprenticeship Programs: Establish apprenticeship programs to attract and train individuals who are new to the industry. Collaborate with local trade schools or vocational programs to create structured apprenticeship opportunities that combine classroom learning with on-the-job training. c. Mentorship Programs: Implement mentorship programs where experienced employees can guide and mentor less experienced team members. This allows for knowledge transfer, skill development, and accelerated learning. d. Collaboration with Educational Institutions: Foster partnerships with educational institutions, such as community colleges or technical schools. Provide input on curriculum development, offer guest lectures, or sponsor projects to create a talent pipeline directly from educational programs. Incorporating technology and automation into your operations can help mitigate labor shortages by increasing efficiency and productivity. Consider the following approaches: a. Streamline Processes: Evaluate your existing workflows and identify areas where technology can streamline processes. Automate repetitive tasks, utilize project management software, and adopt digital tools that optimize productivity. b. Implement Robotics and Automation: Explore the use of robotics and automation technologies to augment your workforce. Identify tasks that can be automated or streamlined through the use of robotics, artificial intelligence, or machine learning. c. Leverage Remote Work and Virtual Collaboration: Embrace remote work opportunities and virtual collaboration tools. This allows you to tap into a larger talent pool and engage skilled workers who may not be located in your immediate area. Building strong relationships with industry partners can help overcome labor shortages by creating opportunities for collaboration and resource sharing. Consider the following strategies: a. Subcontracting and Outsourcing: Collaborate with subcontractors or outsource certain tasks to specialized firms or contractors. This can help alleviate the pressure of labor shortages by leveraging their expertise and resources. b. Strategic Partnerships: Establish strategic partnerships with other companies or contractors in your industry. By sharing resources, collaborating on projects, or cross-training employees, you can overcome labor shortages and ensure successful project delivery. c. Professional Networking: Attend industry conferences, trade shows, and networking events to connect with other professionals in your field. Engage in knowledge-sharing, build relationships, and explore potential collaborations or talent-sharing opportunities. While it is essential to attract new talent, it is equally important to retain and engage your existing employees. Fostering a positive work environment and providing opportunities for growth can help minimize turnover and maintain a skilled workforce. Consider the following retention strategies: a. Competitive Compensation and Benefits: Regularly review and adjust compensation packages to remain competitive in the market. Provide attractive benefits, such as healthcare, retirement plans, and employee wellness programs. b. Recognition and Rewards: Implement employee recognition programs to acknowledge and appreciate exceptional performance. Offer incentives, rewards, or career advancement opportunities to motivate and retain talented employees. c. Professional Development Opportunities: Provide ongoing professional development opportunities to help employees enhance their skills and knowledge. Offer training programs, workshops, certifications, or educational reimbursement to support their career growth. d. Foster a Positive Company Culture: Create a positive work environment that fosters teamwork, open communication, and employee engagement. Encourage a healthy work-life balance and prioritize employee well-being. In conclusion, navigating labor shortages requires a multi-faceted approach that focuses on enhancing recruitment efforts, investing in training and development, embracing technology and automation, fostering relationships with industry partners, and retaining and engaging existing employees. By implementing these strategies, companies and contractors can overcome labor shortages, attract skilled workers, and continue to deliver successful projects, even when the talent pool is not always full.'}]

'language': 'en', 'pageNumber': 0, 'neatVersion': '3.3b', 'inputText': 'In the ever-evolving landscape of modern business, technology is the driving force behind innovation and growth. Whether you’re a small startup or a multinational corporation, harnessing the power of technology can elevate your business game and position you for success. In this article, we’ll explore how technology can transform your business operations and highlight the importance of expert support to ensure a seamless technological journey. Embracing Digital Transformation Digital transformation is more than just a buzzword; it’s a fundamental shift in the way businesses operate and deliver value to customers. Embracing digital transformation involves integrating digital technologies into all aspects of your business, from customer interactions to back-end processes. For instance, adopting cloud computing solutions allows for flexible scalability and cost-effectiveness in managing data and applications. This, in turn, frees up capital that can be invested in other critical areas of your business. To successfully navigate this transformation, many companies rely on expert support from professionals who understand the intricacies of digital adoption and can guide them through the process. Enhancing Efficiency with Automation Efficiency is key in today’s fast-paced business world, and automation is a powerful tool for achieving it. By automating repetitive and time-consuming tasks, you can significantly improve productivity and reduce the risk of errors. Automation can be applied across various departments, from finance and human resources to customer service and marketing. For instance, marketing automation tools can streamline lead generation, nurture customer relationships, and optimize campaign performance. However, implementing automation effectively often requires expert guidance to ensure that the chosen solutions align with your specific business goals and processes. Data-Driven Decision-Making Data is a valuable asset in the digital age, and leveraging it for informed decision-making can give your business a competitive edge. Advanced analytics tools can sift through vast amounts of data to identify trends, customer preferences, and emerging opportunities. This insight allows you to make data-driven decisions that can steer your business in the right direction. But managing and interpreting data effectively can be complex, which is where expert support comes into play. Data professionals can design data strategies, implement analytics solutions, and provide actionable insights that guide your decision-making process and help you stay ahead in your industry. Strengthening Customer Engagement In today’s market, customer engagement is crucial for building brand loyalty and increasing customer retention. Technology solutions like customer relationship management (CRM software can help you manage and nurture customer relationships effectively. CRM systems allow you to centralize customer data, track interactions, and provide personalized experiences. These solutions can also help you identify opportunities for upselling and cross-selling by understanding your customers’ needs and preferences. To maximize the benefits of CRM, businesses often seek expert support to configure the software, ensure data accuracy, and develop strategies that align with their unique customer base. The Role of Strategic IT Support As you embark on your journey to harness the power of technology, it’s essential to recognize the critical role of strategic IT support. Your IT infrastructure is the backbone of your technological ecosystem, and any disruptions or inefficiencies can impact your business’s operations and productivity. Strategic IT support encompasses a range of services, including hardware and software maintenance, security measures, troubleshooting, and technology infrastructure planning. IT professionals with expertise in these areas can ensure that your technology operates smoothly, address technical issues promptly, and provide guidance on technology investments. Whether it’s optimizing your network performance, protecting your data from cyber threats, or helping you transition to new technology platforms, strategic IT support is essential to keep your business running efficiently. The Future of Business Growth In conclusion, harnessing the power of technology is not just a choice but a necessity for businesses aiming to stay competitive and thrive in the digital age. Embracing digital transformation, automating processes, making data-driven decisions, and strengthening customer engagement are essential steps in elevating your business game. However, it’s equally important to have expert support throughout your technological journey. Whether you’re implementing new technologies, analyzing data, or ensuring the smooth operation of your IT infrastructure, professionals with the right expertise can make all the difference in your business’s success. As you navigate the ever-changing landscape of technology, remember that technology is not just a tool; it’s an enabler of innovation, efficiency, and growth. By embracing it fully and seeking expert support where needed, you can elevate your business game and position your company for a brighter future in the digital era.'}]

Whether you’re an avid poker player or a casual game night enthusiast, ensuring that the deck is not stacked against you is important. Marked cards can give certain players an unfair advantage, compromising the integrity of the game. Many gamblers are purchasing it so they can use it when they gamble. Here, we will explore several techniques that can help you identify these deceptive devices and level the playing field for everyone involved. The first and simplest technique to detect marked cards is through visual inspection. Take a few moments to examine the deck before the game begins carefully. Look for any irregularities in the design, such as variations in color or pattern on the back of the cards. Pay close attention to subtle markings or scratches that might indicate tampering. During gameplay, observe how your opponents handle their cards. Keep an eye out for any suspicious behavior, like excessive shuffling or unusual card placements. Trust your instincts if something feels off – intuition can be a valuable tool in detecting foul play. Card shining is a technique used to detect marked cards in a game. It involves using light and reflection to reveal any hidden markings on the surface of the playing cards. This method is particularly effective for detecting invisible ink marks or subtle alterations that may be present. You will need a strong light source, such as a flashlight or lamp to perform Card Shining. Hold the card at an angle and shine the light across its surface. By doing so, any irregularities or discrepancies in the design should become apparent. The key to successful Card Shining lies in observing how the light interacts with different areas of the card. A technique that can be used to detect marked cards in a game is the water drop test. This method involves placing a small droplet of water on the surface of each card and observing how it behaves. When a deck of playing cards is manufactured, the paper stock is typically treated with a special coating that makes it resistant to liquid absorption. Suppose a card has been marked, either by someone applying substances or using invisible ink. In that case, the water droplet will behave differently on that particular card than others in the deck. If a card has been marked, the water droplet may spread out quickly or bead up instead of being absorbed into the paper. This abnormal behavior can indicate that there are markings present on the surface of the card. The most reliable technique to detect marked cards in a game is through the use of UV light. This method involves examining the playing cards under ultraviolet light to reveal any invisible marks or symbols that may have been added. UV light test works by illuminating any hidden markings on the card’s surface, often made using special ink or substances that reflect UV light. By shining a UV flashlight or lamp onto the cards, players can easily identify if there are any alterations or additions to them. The advantage of this method is that it can quickly and discreetly detect any marked cards without arousing suspicion. It allows players to maintain fairness and ensure an enjoyable gaming experience. While these techniques can help detect marked cards, it’s important to note that experienced cheaters may employ sophisticated methods that are harder to detect. Therefore, vigilance and regular checks during gameplay remain essential in preventing cheating incidents. By incorporating these detection techniques into your gameplay routine, you can minimize the risk of falling victim to unfair practices. If you’ve ever played the classic Snake Game on your Google search page, you know how addictive and fun it can be. In this blog post, we will walk you through everything you need to know about using mods in Google Snake Game. Maintaining your Google Snake Game with mods is essential for a smooth and enjoyable gaming experience. We’ll discuss how to keep your mods updated, ensure game performance and stability, and know when it’s time to uninstall a mod. Whether you’re a seasoned Snake Game player or new to the world of mods, this blog post will equip you with the knowledge and tools to enhance your Google Snake Game experience. So let’s dive in and discover the exciting world of mods in Google Snake Game! Google Snake Game is a modern twist on the classic Snake Game that many of us have played on our old Nokia phones. This addictive game can now be enjoyed directly on your Google search page, providing endless hours of entertainment. To access Google Snake Game, simply open your web browser and go to the Google search page. Type “Google Snake Game” into the search bar, and you will see the game appear as a search result. Click on the “Play” button, and you’re ready to start playing! The objective of Google Snake Game is to control a snake on the screen and guide it to eat as many apples as possible. As the snake eats the apples, it grows longer, making it more challenging to navigate the screen without hitting the walls or its own body. The goal is to achieve the highest score possible before the snake collides with an obstacle. Controlling the snake in Google Snake Game is simple. You can use the arrow keys on your keyboard to move the snake up, down, left, or right. The snake moves continuously in the direction you choose until you change its direction or it collides with an obstacle. As you progress in the game and the snake grows longer, maneuvering becomes more challenging. You must avoid hitting the walls or the snake’s own body, as this will result in a game over. Google Snake Game keeps track of your score as you play. Each apple you eat adds points to your score. The more apples you consume, the higher your score will be. You can challenge yourself to beat your previous high score or compete with friends and family to see who can achieve the highest score. Google Snake Game also features leaderboards where you can compare your score with other players around the world. This adds a competitive element to the game and motivates players to improve their skills. In addition to the classic mode, Google Snake Game offers different game modes and challenges to keep the gameplay fresh and exciting. These modes may introduce variations in gameplay mechanics, such as time limits, different obstacles, or additional power-ups. Exploring these different modes can add a new level of fun and challenge to your Snake Game experience. Now that we have covered the basics of Google Snake Game, let’s delve into the world of mods and discover how they can enhance your gameplay. Google Snake Game mods are modifications or enhancements made to the original game to provide additional features, customization options, and improved gameplay experiences. These mods allow you to personalize your Snake Game and tailor it to your preferences. In this section, we will explore what mods are and how they can enhance your Google Snake Game experience. Mods, short for modifications, are user-created alterations to a game that can range from simple tweaks to extensive changes. In the context of Google Snake Game, mods can introduce new gameplay mechanics, graphics enhancements, additional power-ups, different themes, and much more. These modifications can transform the game and give it a fresh and unique feel. Mods enhance gameplay by offering new challenges, improving game mechanics, and providing customization options. They can introduce new levels, obstacles, or game modes that add variety and excitement to your Snake Game sessions. Mods can also enhance the visual appeal of the game with improved graphics, animations, and themes. There are numerous mods available for Google Snake Game, created by talented developers and enthusiasts from the gaming community. Let’s explore some of the popular mods that have gained popularity among Snake Game players: “Speed Boost”: This mod increases the speed of your snake, making the game more fast-paced and challenging. “Multiplayer Mode”: This mod allows you to play Google Snake Game with friends or other players online, adding a competitive element to the gameplay. “Power-up Bonanza”: This mod introduces various power-ups throughout the game, such as invincibility, extra lives, or temporary speed boosts, enhancing the excitement and strategic elements of the game. “Retro Theme”: This mod replaces the game’s graphics with a nostalgic retro theme, giving it a vintage arcade feel. “Obstacle Course”: This mod introduces intricate mazes and obstacles that you must navigate through, testing your skills and agility. Finding mods for Google Snake Game is relatively easy, thanks to the active modding community. Here are some popular platforms and websites where you can discover and download mods: Snake Game Mod Repository: This dedicated website hosts a wide range of mods for Google Snake Game. It allows users to upload and share their creations, making it a hub for mod enthusiasts. Gaming Forums: Online gaming forums, such as Reddit’s gaming communities or dedicated Snake Game forums, often have sections dedicated to mods. Here, you can find recommendations, discussions, and links to download mods. Modding Communities: There are communities and websites specifically focused on game modding. These communities often have dedicated sections for Google Snake Game mods, where you can find a variety of options. Developer Websites: Some mod creators have their own websites or blogs where they showcase their mods. Visiting these websites can give you access to unique and specialized mods. Now that you have an understanding of Google Snake Game mods and where to find them, let’s move on to the next section and learn how to install these mods to enhance your gaming experience. Installing mods for Google Snake Game allows you to customize and enhance your gameplay experience. In this section, we will guide you through the process of installing mods step-by-step, ensuring that you can enjoy the full potential of these modifications. Before installing any mods, it is essential to back up your game data to prevent any potential loss or conflicts. Follow these steps to back up your Google Snake Game data: Locate the game data folder: The game data folder is typically located in the “AppData” or “Application Support” directory on your computer. You can find it by searching for “Google Snake Game” in the file explorer or by checking the game’s installation directory. Make a copy of the game data folder: Right-click on the game data folder and select “Copy.” Then, navigate to a safe location, such as your desktop or an external storage device, and right-click to paste the copied folder. By backing up your game data, you can easily restore your original game if any issues arise during the mod installation process. Now that you have backed up your game data, let’s proceed with the installation of mods for Google Snake Game. Here’s a step-by-step guide: Find the desired mod: Use the websites and platforms mentioned earlier to find the mod you want to install. Ensure that the mod is compatible with the version of Google Snake Game you have. Download the mod files: Locate the download link for the mod file and click on it to initiate the download. Save the file to a location on your computer where you can easily access it. Extract the mod files (if necessary : If the mod file is in a compressed format (such as .zip or .rar , use a file extraction tool like WinRAR or 7-Zip to extract the contents of the file to a new folder. Even today, some still look at these ancient practices for understanding how mind-expanding substances can be good for us. Now that we’ve established the significance of the engine temperature sensor, let’s delve into the steps you should take to prepare your vehicle’s cooling system for extreme tourism: Before embarking on any journey, it’s essential to ensure that your vehicle’s cooling system is in top-notch condition. The two winners, siblings from Jena, are Jena High School student Payton Girlinghouse and Jena Junior High School student Owen Girlinghouse, whose parents are Kurt and Deborah Girlinghouse. The following are the winning essays: The Greatest Attributes of Our Democracy By Payton Girlinghouse Democracy, as a system of authority, embodies the principles of freedom, equality and justice. In the grand tapestry of political systems, democracy stands out as a beacon of hope, offering numerous attributes that make it a cherished form of government. In this essay, we will explore some of the greatest attributes of our democracy and why it is essential, especially for high school students, to understand and appreciate them. One of the most significate attributes of our democracy is the emphasis it places on individual liberty and freedom. In a democratic society, citizens enjoy fundamental rights like freedom of speech, religion and assembly. High school students, in particular, benefit from these liberties, as they allow for the exploration of ideas, the pursuit of education and the development of critical thinking skills. Democracy ensures that your voice matters, enabling you to express your opinions and beliefs without fear of restriction or prosecution. Our democracy backs the principle of equal representation. Through regular elections, every citizen has the opportunity to participate in the decision-making process. This element ensures that no one group or individual can hold unchecked power for too long. For high school students, this means that your voice is heard, even if you are not of voting age yet. Your concerns and needs can be advocated for by elected officials who represent your interest. Democracy places a strong importance on accountability and the rule of law. Elected officials are accountable to the people they serve and they must operate within the structure of the law. This trait ensures that those in power are held responsible for their actions and decisions. For high school students, this means learning about the importance of ethics and integrity in leadership, skills that are crucial for future civic engagement and responsible citizenship. An essential attribute of democracy is the protection of minority rights. In a diverse society like ours, this ensures that even small or marginalized groups have a voice and are protected from the tyranny of the majority. For high school students, this is a valuable lesson in tolerance and empathy, teaching us to appreciate and respect differences in opinions, cultures and backgrounds. Democracy’s ability to adapt and evolve is another significant attribute. It allows for the peaceful transition of power and the inclusion of new ideas and policies as the needs of society change. For high school students, this serves as a reminder that change is possible through peaceful means, encouraging advances and the pursuit of solutions to the world’s problems through the democratic process. In conclusion, the greatest attributes of our democracy – individual liberty, equal representation, accountability, protection of minority rights and adaptability – form the foundation of a just and inclusive society. As high school students, understanding and appreciating these attributes is essential, as they provide the outline for our civil liberties, civic participation and the promise of a brighter future. Democracy, as imperfect as it may be, is a system worth upholding, cherishing and working to improve. It is our responsibility to ensure that these attributes continue to thrive, fostering a society where every voice counts and every citizen can contribute to shaping a better world. How Are You Inspired By America? By Owen Girlinghouse America, the land of dreams, opportunities and variety, has always inspired me, even as an eighth-grader. As a young student, I find inspiration in various features of this great nation, from its history to its values and the stories of individuals who have achieved remarkable feats. Here’s how America inspires me: America’s core values of freedom and equal opportunity are a constant source of inspiration. The idea that all people are created equal and have the right to life, liberty and the pursuit of happiness echoes deeply with me. It reminds me that regardless of where I come from or who I am, I have the potential to achieve my dreams through hard work and determination. America’s history is filled with stories of individuals who have overcome adversity and achieved great things. The founding fathers who drafted the Constitution to civil rights inspire me to believe in the power of ideas and the importance of standing up for what is right. America’s cultural variety is like a mixture of different backgrounds and traditions. This variety inspires me to embrace and celebrate differences. It teaches me that by learning from people of various cultures, I can become a more open-minded and compassionate individual. America is a hub of innovation and creativity. The stories of inventors like Thomas Edison and entrepreneurs like Steve Jobs, show me that with creativity and dedication, I can turn my ideas into reality. This inspires me to explore my interests and think outside the box. America is also a place where people often extend a helping hand to those in need. Acts of kindness and community service inspire me to be a better person and contribute positively to my community. I see the importance of giving back and making a difference in the lives of others. America’s efforts in environmental conservation and sustainability inspire me to be more conscious of our planet’s well-being. I believe in the importance of protecting our environment for future generations and America’s initiatives in the regards for the world. In conclusion, as an eighth-grader, America inspires me in numerous ways, from its values of freedom and likeness to its rich history, cultural variety and commitment to innovation and creativity. These inspirations fuel my dreams and goals, encouraging me to work hard, make a positive impact on my community and strive for a better future. 'neatVersion': '3.3b', 'inputText': 'There is a crisis with American newspapers and other forms of local journalism. In recent years, the newspaper industry has faced a number of challenges, including declining print readership, declining advertising revenue, increasing costs and competition from digital media. As a result, many newspapers have been forced to cut staff, reduce the number of print editions, or shut down entirely. This has led to a decline in local news coverage and a reduction in the number of reporters covering important issues in communities across the United States. This has given rise to “news deserts” which are communities that have limited or no access to local news and information. These areas are often rural or low-income communities. In news deserts, residents may have difficulty accessing important information about local government, events, or community issues. Without access to local news and information, residents may be less informed about important issues, less engaged in their communities, and less likely to participate in civic life. This can have negative consequences for democracy, as it becomes more difficult for citizens to hold elected officials accountable and to make informed decisions about issues that affect their lives. Simultaneously there is the rising threat of “pink slime news” spreading in news deserts. Pink slime journalism is a pejorative term used to describe a style of sensationalist and unethical journalism that is funded with dark money and is focused on news stories that are biased towards a conservative pro-business viewpoint, often with little regard for journalistic ethics or standards. The term was popularized in 2012 after a controversy surrounding the use of a meat product called pink slime in some fast-food chains hamburgers. These pink slime newspapers may focus on issues such as race, LGBTQ, immigration, gun control, or abortion, often with a sensational and radical conservative slant. Critics of pink slime newspapers argue that they undermine the credibility of journalism and contribute to a climate of misinformation and polarized politics. They may also have a negative impact on local communities, as residents may be exposed to biased or incomplete reporting on important issues. Guest: Priyanjana Bengani is a Tow Computational Fellow at Columbia Journalism School s Tow Center for Digital Journalism. The Source is a live call-in program airing Mondays through Thursdays from 12-1 p.m. Leave a message before the program at (210 615-8982. During the live show, call 833-877-8255, email thesource@tpr.org or tweet@TPRSource. *This interview will be recorded on Thursday April 13.'}]

He was born in Kinston, North Carolina, in 1955 and became the first basketball player from Kinston to make it to the major league. Before the NBA, he was most known as a star player for the Charlotte 49ers from 1973-1977. As a UNC Charlotte student, he majored in Black Literature and Geography, with a focus on basketball and sports-related activities. In 1977, he led the Charlotte 49ers to the NCAA Final Four Tournament making it the first time the 49ers would earn this achievement. That same year, he graduated and retired his #33 jersey for the 49ers. Maxwell was selected by the Boston Celtics in the 1977 NBA draft, making him the 12th overall pick in the draft. It wasn t until his second season when he began to make an impact in the industry. His skills, personality and performance on the court were well received and catapulted him to the 1981 NBA Finals. The Boston Celtics would go on to win the NBA Championship that year. In 1985, Maxwell was traded to the LA Clippers, where he would play for almost two seasons. Shortly after, he signed with the Houston Rockets for the 1987-1988 season and eventually retired from the NBA after an 11 season career. Aside from his iconic basketball career, Maxwell also had an interest in radio broadcasting and sports media. Back in 2001, he got his start in broadcasting by announcing Boston Celtic games alongside Sean Grande. Maxwell is now married and is a father to four children. In 2020, Cedric Maxwell was inducted into the Charlotte 49ers Hall Of Fame. Today he resides in Boston, Massachusetts, where he hosts a podcast titled The Cedric Maxwell Podcast, where he interviews many former NBA affiliates and discusses many of his life stories. Cedric Maxwell will always be remembered for his performance in the NBA and as a Charlotte 49er. If you’re considering a career in the heating, ventilation, and air conditioning (HVAC industry, you might be wondering what kind of education and training you need to become a qualified HVAC technician. In this article, we’ll explore the various schooling options available to you and how they can benefit your career. First of all, it’s worth noting that there are no federal education requirements for HVAC technicians. However, most employers prefer to hire technicians who have completed some form of formal training or apprenticeship program. This is because HVAC systems are becoming increasingly complex, and employers want to ensure that their technicians have the knowledge and skills necessary to keep up with the latest technologies. One option for HVAC technician schooling is a certificate or diploma program. These programs typically take between six months and one year to complete and provide students with the foundational knowledge and hands-on training they need to start their careers. Certificate and diploma programs cover topics such as refrigeration, electrical systems, HVAC design, and troubleshooting techniques. Another option is an associate degree program, which typically takes two years to complete. Associate degree programs offer a more comprehensive education, covering not only the technical aspects of HVAC systems but also business management, communication, and customer service skills. This makes graduates of associate degree programs more attractive to employers who are looking for technicians who can not only repair and maintain HVAC systems but also interact effectively with customers and manage their own workload. Finally, some HVAC technicians choose to pursue apprenticeships instead of formal education programs. Apprenticeships involve on-the-job training with an experienced HVAC technician, supplemented by classroom instruction. Apprenticeships typically take between three and five years to complete, and graduates are considered journeymen who are qualified to work independently. No matter which type of schooling you choose, it’s important to select a program that is accredited by a recognized organization such as HVAC Excellence or the Partnership for Air-Conditioning, Heating, and Refrigeration Accreditation (PAHRA . Accredited programs have been evaluated for quality and adherence to industry standards, ensuring that you receive a rigorous education that will prepare you for a successful career. International travel can be an exciting and enriching experience, allowing you to explore new cultures, try new foods, and make unforgettable memories. However, it’s important to understand that international travel comes with its own unique set of challenges and considerations. In this article, we’ll go over some of the key things you should know about international travel. One of the most important things to consider when traveling internationally is your passport and visa requirements. Different countries have different requirements when it comes to these documents, so it’s essential to research the specific requirements for your destination well in advance of your trip. Another thing to keep in mind when traveling internationally is the potential for language barriers. Depending on where you’re traveling, you may encounter people who speak a different language than you. It’s a good idea to learn some basic phrases in the local language before your trip, as well as carrying a translation app or guidebook with you. When traveling internationally, it’s important to take extra precautions to protect your health and safety. This might include getting vaccinations, packing a first aid kit, and researching potential health risks in your destination. You should also familiarize yourself with the local laws and customs to avoid any potential legal issues. Another important consideration when traveling internationally is money. You’ll need to research the local currency and exchange rates before your trip, and decide whether to use credit cards or cash while abroad. It’s also a good idea to notify your bank and credit card companies of your travel plans to avoid any issues with fraud protection. Finally, it’s important to be aware of the potential for culture shock when traveling internationally. Different cultures may have different customs and ways of doing things, which can take some getting used to. Try to be open-minded and respectful of local customs, and do your best to adapt to the local culture. Fridays are a special treat, featuring Oldies rock and roll chart-toppers from the 50s, 60s, 70s, and a dash of the 80s. The event is scheduled to take place on February 23, 2024, and will mark a historic moment in recognition of Dr. Nero’s groundbreaking contributions to education and leadership. Dr. Donnie Nero, who served as the first African-American president of a non-historically black institution in the state of Oklahoma, has left an indelible mark on Connors State College and the broader educational community. His career, which began in the Sapulpa Public Schools and ascended to the presidency of Connors State College, is characterized by a commitment to excellence and service. The dedication ceremony will commence at 10:00 am in the A.D. Stone Student Union Ballroom on Connors State College’s Warner campus. The event will feature keynote speakers, tributes to Dr. Nero’s legacy, and a symbolic unveiling of the newly named Dr. Donnie Nero Fine Arts Center. President Ramming expresses the college’s gratitude for Dr. Nero’s transformative leadership, stating, “This dedication is a testament to Dr. Nero’s unwavering commitment to not only Connors State College, but education as a whole across Oklahoma. The Dr. Donnie Nero Fine Arts Center will stand as a lasting tribute to his legacy and a source of inspiration for current and future generations of students.” Dr. Nero’s achievements include serving on the Governor’s “Edge” Task Force, earning numerous accolades such as the Phi Theta Kappa International Shirley B. Gordon Award of Distinction, and founding the Oklahoma African-American Educators Hall of Fame in 2010. His induction into various halls of fame, including the Oklahoma Higher Education Hall of Fame, reflects his lasting impact on education in Oklahoma. The Connors State College community invites alumni, friends, and the public to join in celebrating this momentous occasion. For more information about the dedication ceremony or to RSVP, please contact Brandy McElyea by emailing brandy.mcelyea@connorsstate.edu or calling (918 463-6343.'}]
